                            <span class="footer-left-padding"></span>Surat - 395 006,<br>  <span class="footer-left-padding"></span>Gujrat, India.
                        </p>
                        <i class="fa fa-mobile"></i><a href="tel: +91 7202022022" title="Sales Enquiry" style="color:#444;z-index:999;position:relative"> &nbsp; +91 72020 22022</a><br>
                        <i class="fa fa-mobile"></i><a href="tel: +91 9316456429" title="Sales Enquiry" style="color:#444;z-index:999;position:relative"> &nbsp; +91 93164 56429</a><br>

                        <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> <a href="mailto:sales@erooftech.com" style="color:#444;z-index:999;position:relative">sales@erooftech.com</a> <br>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix"> </div>
